{"type":"click","text":"Option A: Guide then Explore\n        \n          \n            Section 1\n            Good for this moment\n            4 recipe cards based on breakfast/lunch/dinner/snack time.\n          \n\n          \n            Section 2\n            \n              \n                Start personalizing your feed\n                Explain why recommendations are limited and invite the user to unlock better results.\n                \n                  Set preferences\n                  Save recipes you like\n                \n              \n              \n                Unlocks\n                Because you saved...\n                Taste-based picks\n                Time-aware meals\n              \n            \n          \n\n          \n            Section 3\n            Explore by taste\n            Clickable cuisines and moods to help the user create their first signal.\n            \n              Italian\n              Spicy\n              Vegetarian\n              High Protein\n              Comfort Food\n            \n            \n              Recipe preview\n              Recipe preview\n              Recipe preview\n            \n          \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      Option A\n      Section 2 is an onboarding/CTA panel. Section 3 becomes an interactive exploration block. Best when we want cold-start users to do one clear next step.","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1774010435966}
